graph TD
    START([START]) --> LLM_CALL[llm_call Node]
    
    LLM_CALL --> COND{should_continue?}
    
    COND -->|Has tool_calls| TOOL_NODE[tool_node]
    COND -->|No tool_calls| END_NODE([END])
    
    TOOL_NODE --> LLM_CALL
    
    style START fill:#90EE90
    style END_NODE fill:#FFB6C1
    style LLM_CALL fill:#87CEEB
    style TOOL_NODE fill:#DDA0DD
    style COND fill:#FFD700
